{{Infobox play | name = Buy the Bi and Bye | image = | alt = | caption = | writer = [[Felton Perry]] | chorus = | characters = | mute = | setting = Theater | premiere = 1976 | place = [[Los Angeles]], [[California]], United States | orig_lang = [[English language|English]] | series = | subject = | genre = [[Satire]] | web = }}
'''''Buy the Bi and Bye''''' is an American play written by [[Felton Perry]] that was first staged in 1976 at the Actor's Theater in Los Angeles, California.<ref name=LAT>{{cite newspaper|newspaper=[[Los Angeles Times]]|title=Street Life Inside and Outside LATC : Theater explores, with uneven results, multiethnic community in which it lives|date=March 12, 1989|author=Drake, Sylvie|url=http://articles.latimes.com/1989-03-12/entertainment/ca-1030_1_latino-theater}}</ref>
==Plot== A group of mostly [[African Americans|black]] actors gather at a theater to read through a fictional play called ''Killing Flo'' by a [[schizophrenia|schizophrenic]] [[White Americans|white]] writer-director.
==Reception== The ''Progress Bulletin'' [[newspaper]] praised the 1976 premiere staging of the play calling it an "offbeat and hilarious black satire with a zinging performance by [[Ron Thompson (actor)|Ron Thompson]]."<ref name=PB>{{cite newspaper|newspaper=Progress Buelltin|title=Entertainment In The Valley|location=[[Pomona, California]]|date=7 February 1976|page=28|url=https://www.newspapers.com/image/71730766/}}</ref>
When the play was later performed in 1986 the ''[[Los Angeles Times]]'' wrote "The voice of a keenly observant satirist is heard throughout "Buy the Bi and Bye," at the Richmond Shepard. Yet Felton Perry's play isn't as sharp as it must have been 10 years ago at Los Angeles Actors' Theatre."<ref name=LAT2>{{cite web|title='Buy The Bi And Bye' Gets A Bit Stale|date=June 20, 1986|author=Shirley, Don|url=http://articles.latimes.com/1986-06-20/entertainment/ca-11564_1_black-family|work=[[Los Angeles Times]]}}</ref><ref name=LAT3>{{cite newspaper|newspaper=[[Los Angeles Times]]|agency=[[Newspapers.com]]|url=https://www.newspapers.com/image/173624038/|title='Buy The Bi And Buy' Gets A Bit Stale|author=Shirley, Don|location=[[Los Angeles]], [[California]]|date=20 June 1986|page=133}}</ref>
